      "dcterms:description": "The five statutory Inner London boroughs south of the River Thames, as defined by Schedule 1 of the London Government Act 1963 (c.33). This is not a statutory administrative unit in itself — the region boundary is derived by combining the five qualifying borough boundaries.",
      "inclusionRule": "Statutory Inner London boroughs south of the River Thames per Schedule 1 of the London Government Act 1963 (c.33). See boroughInclusionRule in the ConceptScheme node for full criteria and alternatives considered."
    },
