        "changes": [
          "Added formal boroughInclusionRule to ConceptScheme node, citing London Government Act 1963 (c.33) Schedule 1 as the authority for borough inclusion.",
          "Removed Croydon, Bromley, Merton, Sutton, and Kingston from containsPlace on the south-london region node — these are Outer London boroughs outside scope.",
          "Updated south-london region node boundarySource to cite the 1963 Act rather than the ONS sub-region code.",
          "Added inclusionRule property to south-london region node.",
          "Added explicitExclusions, greenwichNote, and alternativeDefinitionsConsidered to boroughInclusionRule for transparency.",
          "Updated coverage description in _meta."
